<ulink url="http://ask.slashdot.org/story/12/07/12/1431210/ask-slashdot-how-do-you-track-bugs-for-personal-software-projects" >Ask Slashdot: How do you track bugs for personal software projects?</ulink>, or <ulink
url="http://www.webresourcesdepot.com/9-free-and-open-source-bug-tracking-softwares/"
>this list at WebResourcesDepot</ulink>.</emphasis></para>
